\v 30 Benaiah \x + \xo 23:30 \xt Judg. 12:13, 15; 1 Chr. 27:14 \x*of Pirathon, Hiddai of the brooks of \x + \xo 23:30 \xt Josh. 24:30; Judg. 2:9\x*Gaash,
